191 吨，有色副产金完成 25.768 吨。据中国黄金协会工作人员介绍，因金矿企业盈利空间增加，有空间进一步降低入选品位，使得黄金产量进一步增长。黄金消费市场分化！金饰消费「遇冷」，更低溢价的金条、金币受「热捧」 | 每经网 (nbd.com.cn) 黄金价格高位盘整，卖黄金热潮来了，业内人士提醒短期追涨应保持谨慎，如何看待金价后续行情？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-cad5dbc0e2ff894dd6e398de40d1a5c5_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "8 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/654260117"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IubXwjaPe1ZdjEAMaCTEwNzY2ODg4NSCurLGxBjAAOC5AK3IJNjU0MjYwMTE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1714265793.678991", "card_id": "Q_653889479", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 113}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价郑保瑞执导，古天乐、洪金宝主演的犯罪动作电影《九龙城寨之围城》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-17eef19b1c08a6977f7dd7631012c7f0_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "8 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/653889479"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIubXwjaPe1ZdjEAMaCTEwNzU4NjQ2NiC+jJ+xBjAAOJEBQCxyCTY1Mzg4OTQ3OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1714265793.679181", "card_id": "Q_650453947", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 209}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "文笔挑战：「月色清明花满树，________」，你会怎么接下一句？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-da6a28c0b0c89dd454f99bb40e2786fe_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "7 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/650453947"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIubXwjaPe1ZdjEAMaCTEwNjgyMzIxMiC9iZCwBjAAON0BQC1yCTY1MDQ1Mzk0N3gAqgEJYmlsb